{
  "name": "Uzumaki Stubbornness",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Uzumaki.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your determination and chakra reserves are powerful enough to keep you standing despite your body suffering grievous injuries. When you fall to or below 0 hit points, you may as a reaction inject chakra throughout your body forcing yourself to survive, instead dropping to 1 hit point. You gain an additional reaction which you can only use to cast this jutsu. This additional reaction lasts until the beginning of your next turn. You can cast this Jutsu up to three times per round.</p><p>At the beginning of your next turn, you gain 1 rank of weakened for the next minute as the stress from maintaining consciousness and fighting through the trauma takes its toll on you.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
